    <mainBody>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p><b><u>The Agricultural or Forestry Tractors (Emission of Gaseous and Particulate Pollutants) and Tractor etc (EC Type-Approval) (Amendment) Regulations 2015</u></b></p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p><b>Transposition Note</b><br /><br />Transposition note for the implementation of Commission Directive 2014/43/EU of 18 March 2014 amending Annexes I, II and III to Directive 2000/25/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council on action to be taken against the emission of gaseous and particulate pollutants by engines intended to power agricultural or forestry tractors (“2014/43/EU”), and Commission Directive 2014/44/EU of 18 March 2014 amending Annexes I, II and III to Directive 2003/37/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council on type-approval of agricultural or forestry tractors, their trailers and interchangeable towed machinery, together with their systems, components and separate technical units (“2014/44/EU”). </p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <paragraph>
        <content>
          <p>The Agricultural or Forestry Tractors (Emission of Gaseous and Particulate Pollutants) and Tractor etc (EC Type-Approval) (Amendment) Regulations 2015 do what is necessary to implement the Directives by making consequential changes to domestic legislation to ensure its coherence in the area to which they apply.</p>
          <table uk:widths="1.43in 1.43in 1.46in 1.44in">
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p><b>Article</b></p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><b>Purpose</b></p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><b>Implementation</b></p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><b>Responsibility</b></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 1</p>
                <p>(2014/43/EU)</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Amends Annexes I, II and III of Directive 2000/25/EC which prescribe the information that manufacturers must submit to approval authorities by adding additional information on pollution control devices fitted.</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulation 2</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Secretary of State</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 1 (2014/44/EU)</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Amends Annexes I, II and III of Directive 2003/37/EC which prescribe the information that manufacturers must submit to approval authorities by adding additional information on pollution control devices fitted.</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulation 3</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Secretary of State</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </content>
      </paragraph>
